INSTRUCTIONS:
Download Xampp, press start
Go to volumes, mount
Since you have a mac go on finder and you'll see an IP address under Locations
Go to the htdocs directory
Go to root dir (If theres no root dir make one)
Put the login.php in the root dir
Type your ip address/phpmyadmin and import the sql file (database)
Manually add in a username/password into the db using phpmyadmin
Login by going to your ipaddress/root/login.php